Remember @OceanHealthSg High Strength Omega-3 Vitamin D3 Enriched I told you about?⁣
⁣

⁣
Together with @oceanhealthsg, we are giving away to 3 lucky winners, a bottle of High Strength Omega-3 Vitamin D3-Enriched (60s) each.⁣
⁣
All you have to do is:⁣
1. L I K E this post⁣
2. F O L L O W us @oceanhealthsg & @belandbray⁣
3. C O M M E N T - Share with us how do you keep your loved one healthy, and tag 3 friends! (3 unique friends per comment; multiple entries allowed) ⁣
⁣
Giveaway ends 4 Jun 2020 2359 and winners will be contacted via DM. ⁣
⁣
Each bottle of High Strength Omega-3 Vitamin D3-Enriched (60s) retails at $29.90, and is available at major retail pharmacies and online stores. Don't forget our code <<OCEAKAREN>> till 31 May 2020 to enjoy 35% off @OceanHealthSg's official store @shopee_sg!⁣
